                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "One potential alternative to the presented formula (4) could be to replace each occurrence of "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\chi_{u_i}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " in the last term with "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\chi_T"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". Intuitively, this alternative has the appeal that "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\chi_T"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " can be factored out of the sum, and the remaining formula is totally FX- free within the asset's currency. Since this is what the front office system SOPHIS does in its column \"Result curr. global\", when the global currency is EUR, let us briefly comment on the implied change of meaning. When using "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\chi_T"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " always, the obtained PnL intuitively assumes that each received coupon amount "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "c_{u}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " at some time "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "u"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " is held in cash (not on a bank account, and also not invested in some other asset) between "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "u"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " and "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "T"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". Changes in the FX rate at later time points then induce significant PnL movements to cash amounts that have long left the position under consideration. For example, consider a bond that pays a high coupon rate, so a lot of cash leaves the asset over time. But if the FX rate "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "\\chi"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " sharply increases at time "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "T"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ", all these past cash amounts induce PnL, even though they might have been consumed or spent elsewhere already and should not induce PnL at "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "T"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        533,
                                        2116,
                                        1322
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " anymore."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 2
                },
                {
