                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "The change of the carry PnL part is especially important, if one aggregates several assets to a portfolio and wishes to decompose the PnL of the whole portfolio. It is then well possible that an asset is bought or sold at some time point "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "u"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " in "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "(t,T]"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": ". For instance, it could be that at time "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "u"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " one receives a coupon payment from one asset and uses it to purchase another asset, or it could be that additional money flows into (out of) the asset to increase (reduce) the holdings. In qualitative terms, this is similar to the aforementioned coupon cash outflows, because we have to deal with in- and outflows in our PnL measurement. In order to take such dynamic rebalancings of a whole portfolio "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "P"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " into account in the PnL decomposition, we recommend to split the time period "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        374,
                                        1382,
                                        2118,
                                        2059
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "(t,T]"
